de.must.markup
Class DataList

java.lang.Object
  de.must.markup.Dialog
      de.must.markup.List
          de.must.markup.DataList
All Implemented Interfaces:
Invokable
Direct Known Subclasses:
ColumnDataList, SimpleDataList
public abstract class DataList
extends List

Component for listing data to select entries for further processing. To avoid repeated database inquiry when control comes back from deeper stack invokables, the list is cached.

free

protected void free()
Description copied from class: Dialog
Frees (releases) references caused by this frame, particularly static register entries. To be called via destroy() to prevent multiple call. Override it to do additional releases and don't forget to call super.free() at the end.

Overrides:
free in class Dialog
